From e4d934473efc5f97b1a90caa9ef1bb0267b89633 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Michael Lerman <mlerman@ironscales.com>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 14:28:38 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 6/6] chore: migrate pi deps to @earendil-works scope

The Pi toolkit moved from the @mariozechner org to earendil-works
(github.com/earendil-works/pi). Update peer deps and imports:

- @mariozechner/pi-ai            -> @earendil-works/pi-ai
- @mariozechner/pi-coding-agent  -> @earendil-works/pi-coding-agent

The new pi-ai bundles typebox v1 and re-exports Type, so source Type
from @earendil-works/pi-ai (alongside StringEnum) instead of
@sinclair/typebox; the separate @sinclair/typebox peer is dropped to
avoid two incompatible typebox copies.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
